Description

Here we are creating a Telegram Bot ..
Step 1: Creating a Telegram bot

		Login to your telegram account and go to BotFather	give the following  commands

		/start - to start the BotFather bot

		/newbot - to create you own bot

		give name to your bot like "iknameBot" make sure name ends with bot
    Now you will get a token to access HTTP API. 

Step 2: Install telepot package in python to code the bot in python.

Step 3: Write python  code for the bot and run.

Step 4: Send message to bot and bot will give responses  as written  in code
